WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.480 --> 00:00:02.120
Hey, good morning, family.

00:00:02.530 --> 00:00:11.071
After I did my last video, I think the major thing people wanted to know is, "Do you have a pastor that is a female?

00:00:11.880 --> 00:00:30.920
" Folks, let me tell you like this: in Joel chapter 2, the Bible says that in the last days, "I will pour out my spirit upon your sons and your daughters and on your handmaidens"—and that's a female.

00:00:30.920 --> 00:00:33.663
So we're in those last days.

00:00:34.120 --> 00:00:43.872
Regardless of whether you want to believe that God can use a female or a male, I'm here to say it's all hands on deck.

00:00:43.872 --> 00:01:04.800
If the men are not going to do the job and they're sitting back with their thumb in their nose and being lazy, and the women want to take the baton and say, "Hey, I know that God has called me for such a time as this to lead the people, to help bring prayer in," that's where I'm at.

00:01:05.120 --> 00:01:33.137
If I see the anointing and the presence of God on male or female, I'm going to follow and listen to what they have to say just because of what Joel chapter 2:28 said: "And it shall come to pass afterward that I will pour out my spirit upon all flesh; your sons and your daughters shall prophesy, your old men shall dream dreams, your young men shall see visions.

00:01:33.137 --> 00:01:39.768
And also upon the servants and upon the handmaids in those days will I pour out my spirit.

00:01:39.768 --> 00:01:44.499
" So you see what the word is saying right there?

00:01:44.799 --> 00:01:46.266
That's what I go by.

00:01:46.266 --> 00:02:07.011
I know Paul talks about having women be silent in the church and not interrupting, but I believe as we draw closer to the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ, we are seeing God put His hand of fire even on His sons, His daughters, and on the handmaidens.

00:02:07.486 --> 00:02:09.590
I believe that's what we're seeing right now.

00:02:10.293 --> 00:02:20.129
We can criticize and say, "Well, they shouldn't be in this; women shouldn't do this; women shouldn't do that," but I'm going by Joel chapter 2 in the Old Testament.

00:02:20.404 --> 00:02:25.610
Then we have Acts chapter 2, which says this is that which was spoken by the prophet Joel.

00:02:26.400 --> 00:02:40.519
The Holy Ghost and fire came into the upper room and filled them all with tongues of fire, and the women and the men were speaking with tongues of fire, and the glory of the Lord filled that whole place like a mighty rushing wind.

00:02:40.519 --> 00:02:47.286
So I know what the Lord has shown me concerning these last days.

00:02:47.737 --> 00:03:15.330
From Kathryn Kuhlman to Joyce Meyer to the people that have ministered to me—she talks about the "Battlefield of the Mind" and some amazing things she went through—I look at the people that God is calling up right now.

00:03:15.330 --> 00:03:23.074
Like I said, ladies and gentlemen, it's all hands on deck.

00:03:23.074 --> 00:03:52.017
We have a lot of men that do not have a backbone like a crowbar, who are being limp-wristed, wearing skinny jeans and using fog machines, wanting to follow the crowd—kind of men that don't even know they're metrosexual, that don't even know who they are.

00:04:05.941 --> 00:04:06.266
I identify myself as a man or a woman—or, "Oh, I identify myself as a dog.

00:04:06.266 --> 00:04:27.320
" I heard that kids in these schools were coming to school saying that they identify as a dog or a cat, and they dress up like a dog or a cat before they come to school.

00:04:27.320 --> 00:04:33.947
Folks, we don't even know what we are anymore.

00:04:33.947 --> 00:04:50.735
So God's trying to find somebody that will just say yes without all this religious stuff going, "Well, you know, they can't be used because of their parts.

00:04:50.735 --> 00:05:06.782
" God's saying, "I'm looking for a pure heart," and I can't find one because right now we've got a bunch of knuckleheads that don't even know who they are anymore.

00:05:06.782 --> 00:05:18.340
I'm not going to sit here and criticize and go, "Well, she can't go up there and lead prayer because she's a female.

00:05:18.340 --> 00:05:26.400
" Folks, you're thinking too small for what God's trying to do in these last days.

00:05:26.400 --> 00:05:32.400
God said, "I will pour out my spirit upon all flesh.

00:05:42.339 --> 00:05:42.759
" So that's what I'm looking for.

00:05:42.759 --> 00:06:02.200
If you want to rock in your chair and sit there and criticize everybody who's trying to do something good for God, then you probably shouldn't watch my channel.

00:06:02.200 --> 00:06:12.267
I believe my wife is called; she's my rearguard, my helper, and my friend.

00:06:12.267 --> 00:06:28.248
I've seen an anointing on her: she dreams, she has visions, she sees things, and God uses her just as much as He uses me.

00:06:28.248 --> 00:07:10.500
Yeah, I'm the head of the house, I run our home, I flow with the spirit of the Lord, and I lead my family, but I believe she's my helpmate and she's my friend, and she's here to teach just as much as me.

00:07:10.500 --> 00:07:27.295
This channel is just not my own; He said, "I've called her to walk beside you, not behind you, Brandon.

00:07:27.295 --> 00:07:51.980
" There are people that get all upset about that and say, "Well, women shouldn't do that," but I'm here to tell you you're wrong because I believe with all my heart it's all hands on deck.

00:07:51.980 --> 00:08:05.624
We saw that in scripture right here, Joel chapter 2, right here in black and white.

00:08:05.624 --> 00:08:17.733
In the last days He said, "I'll pour my spirit upon all flesh.

00:08:17.733 --> 00:08:48.160
" So we're going to go with that because Joel prophesied it, and then we see in Acts chapter 2 that this is that which was spoken by the prophet Joel: "In the last days I will pour out my spirit upon all flesh.

00:08:48.160 --> 00:08:56.189
" We're seeing that already, and that was 2,000 years ago.

00:08:56.189 --> 00:09:17.708
So here we are right now in present day, and the Lord tells us, "Brandon, I'm going to do one last call, one major push for a harvest of souls.

00:09:17.708 --> 00:09:20.855
Will you be a part of it?

00:09:20.855 --> 00:09:34.515
I'm just looking for someone who will just say yes, son, who will help me bring in the harvest.

00:09:34.515 --> 00:09:39.665
" I'm saying it from the mountaintops that Jesus Christ is coming.

00:09:49.040 --> 00:10:07.853
The eyes of the Lord are running to and fro throughout the whole earth, looking for a heart who's perfect towards Him, looking for someone that will have a great yielded want-to to say, "Hey God, here am I, send me.

00:10:07.853 --> 00:10:26.800
" Send me to the nations to preach, to teach, to do whatever it takes to bring in the lost.

00:10:29.874 --> 00:10:45.920
I refuse to let the rocks do my job, for it says in the word that if I don't praise Him, the rocks will cry out.

00:10:45.920 --> 00:11:07.426
I'm telling you, God is a God that's worthy to be praised, and I refuse to let the rocks do my job.

00:11:20.310 --> 00:11:20.781
I will praise Him today because He is worthy to be praised.

00:11:20.781 --> 00:11:39.639
Last night at Wednesday night church, the glory came down and the presence of the Lord was so strong you could feel it.

00:11:39.639 --> 00:12:09.520
Whenever you go into a church service and it keeps going and going, and you lose track of time in the glory because everything your spirit ever needs is at His feet, people go, "Well, what time am I going home?

00:12:09.520 --> 00:12:30.269
" If you don't want to sit at His feet, give me the keys and the code and I'll lock up your building for you, because nothing else matters to me.

00:12:30.269 --> 00:12:38.620
There's nothing in this earth that I want more than to sit at His feet.

00:12:38.620 --> 00:13:12.839
You can lose yourself in the numbers and the money because it's what the flesh wants, but as for me and my house, we will serve the Lord with all our hearts, all our minds, all our soul, and all our strength, and we'll love our neighbor as ourselves.

00:13:12.839 --> 00:13:36.434
We'll love those because those two angels that stood over my bed that night said, to make a long story short, what he needs to know is that when he stands before the Father, what he will be judged upon the most is what he did with love.

00:13:54.279 --> 00:13:54.959
How did he love his brother?

00:13:54.959 --> 00:14:12.736
How did he love those around him and treat people with respect and honor?

00:14:12.736 --> 00:14:25.180
What did he do with love beyond anything else?

00:14:25.180 --> 00:14:35.955
It won't be because I gave this amount of money or I did this.

00:14:35.955 --> 00:14:42.729
No, how did you walk in love towards your brethren?

00:14:42.729 --> 00:14:47.994
Love takes no account of a suffered wrong, ladies and gentlemen.

00:14:47.994 --> 00:15:02.771
In the comment section, love takes no account of a suffered wrong—even to a preacher who's talking trash about you behind your back.

00:15:21.874 --> 00:15:22.188
I choose to love.

00:15:22.188 --> 00:15:31.149
I choose to be what Jesus has called me to be in this earth.

00:15:31.149 --> 00:15:39.130
I stay vertical; I refuse to go horizontal.

00:15:53.818 --> 00:15:54.036
I go vertical regardless of people cursing you with their mouth or regardless of people coming on here from the occult.

00:15:56.580 --> 00:15:59.560
It's in Him I move and have my being.

00:15:59.560 --> 00:16:04.160
He is the one I'm after.

00:16:04.160 --> 00:16:27.685
Some of you are just after what you can get on this earth, but everything you achieve, unless it's for Him, it will burn up like chaff before His throne.

00:16:30.600 --> 00:16:41.319
It will either be pure like gold that will stand the fire, or it will be straw and stubble.

00:16:57.440 --> 00:17:11.120
I choose to not lay up my treasures upon this earth because all I know is that when I get on the other side, He's either going to say, "I knew you," or "Depart from me; I never knew you.

00:17:11.120 --> 00:17:28.549
" I heard Benny Hinn say he was on the table having that heart attack and he was in line to go before the Father.

00:17:28.549 --> 00:17:39.940
An organist was playing, and Jesus was standing there greeting the people.

00:17:39.940 --> 00:17:55.666
She would play a certain sound, and the sound was either a welcoming sound or a sound of judgment.

00:17:55.666 --> 00:18:02.656
Either Jesus gave you a nod of "yes" or "no.

00:18:02.656 --> 00:18:26.046
" As Benny Hinn got before the Father, he saw all his works—the healing revivals, the souls that had come in—but over the course of time his heart had become cold to the Father.

00:18:35.390 --> 00:18:39.040
The Lord showed me and He showed my wife, Diana, "Brandon, I'll use whoever I want to.

00:18:39.040 --> 00:18:51.364
Just because you have the anointing and just because you flow under the anointing doesn't mean that I know you.

00:18:51.647 --> 00:18:55.027
" I will use whoever I want.

00:18:55.027 --> 00:19:01.227
The anointing is not about relationship; the anointing is a tool.

00:19:01.227 --> 00:19:25.240
We qualify for the anointing, but He doesn't turn it off because it's a tool, just like this shirt covers me or my shaver shaves my head.

00:19:25.490 --> 00:19:38.926
The anointing is a cloak that helps us to operate in this earth so that we're able to get the job done.

00:19:38.926 --> 00:19:42.370
Does that make sense?

00:19:42.370 --> 00:19:48.025
We are the tool, but we are the glove.

00:19:49.125 --> 00:20:02.200
The Holy Spirit said, "You are the glove; I am the hand that goes in the glove.

00:20:06.746 --> 00:20:10.012
You are always to deflect the glory to the Father.

00:20:10.012 --> 00:20:13.780
" So that's where we are right now.

00:20:13.780 --> 00:20:28.440
In these end times, it's all hands on deck, but just because you have some anointing doesn't mean that He's intimate with you.

00:20:28.440 --> 00:20:34.858
Intimacy is sitting at His feet on a daily basis.

00:20:34.858 --> 00:20:38.208
"Hello, Father, how are you?

00:20:38.208 --> 00:20:43.624
" Don't lose yourself in works, numbers, growth, or money.

00:20:43.624 --> 00:20:46.775
Lose yourself in His breath.

00:20:48.875 --> 00:20:51.571
"Father, I need You; Father, I worship You.

00:20:51.571 --> 00:21:05.138
I want to have a revelation knowledge according to Ephesians, that the eyes of my understanding would be enlightened today.

00:21:05.138 --> 00:21:15.634
" I thank You, Lord, that I sit at Your feet.

00:21:15.634 --> 00:21:32.053
When I sit before You in that day, He either says, "Brandon, I knew you," or "You did a lot on the earth, but I never had a relationship with you.

00:21:32.053 --> 00:21:40.707
" Diana is going to read this to you because it's very important that you understand.

00:21:40.707 --> 00:21:45.132
Oh, it's just about grace, brother?

00:21:45.132 --> 00:22:00.907
Yeah, you're saved by grace through faith, not of works, lest any man should boast; it is a gift of God.

00:22:00.907 --> 00:22:04.453
We understand that, but it's about relationship.

00:22:11.783 --> 00:22:29.880
I want you to meditate on this scripture while I'm trying to bring you to a conclusion of all the things that you think make you qualified.

00:22:29.880 --> 00:22:37.600
I'm taking it all back to a heart thing.

00:22:37.600 --> 00:22:46.740
Holy Communion is holy, but it is an act of worship in my house.

00:22:46.740 --> 00:22:55.456
It's an act of, "God, I love You; I just want to be at Your feet.

00:23:07.280 --> 00:23:07.540
I just want to know You more.

00:23:08.320 --> 00:23:13.990
" I just want a personal relationship with the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:23:13.990 --> 00:23:32.520
Matthew 7:21: "Not everyone that saith unto me, Lord, Lord, shall enter into the kingdom of heaven; but he that doeth the will of my Father which is in heaven.

00:23:32.520 --> 00:23:47.027
Many will say to me in that day, Lord, Lord, have we not prophesied in thy name?

00:23:47.027 --> 00:23:52.300
And in thy name have cast out devils?

00:23:52.300 --> 00:23:58.594
And in thy name done many wonderful works?

00:23:58.594 --> 00:24:14.720
And then will I profess unto them, I never knew you: depart from me, ye that work iniquity.

00:24:17.768 --> 00:24:19.235
" I don't want Him saying that to me.

00:24:19.235 --> 00:24:28.950
It takes some anointing to cast out a devil or raise the dead, but He said, "Depart from me; I never knew you.

00:24:29.880 --> 00:24:31.409
" What is it about?

00:24:31.409 --> 00:24:32.951
It's about relationship.

00:24:32.951 --> 00:24:41.940
It's about sitting at His feet and saying, "Jesus, I love You.

00:24:41.940 --> 00:24:45.386
" Communion with Him—a heart thing.

00:25:02.799 --> 00:25:04.010
For the eyes of the Lord are running to and fro throughout the whole earth, looking for a heart who's perfect toward Him.

00:25:04.010 --> 00:25:16.754
I pray, "Father, if Your eyes are roaming right now, help my heart to be what pleases You today.

00:25:16.754 --> 00:25:24.640
" Help my heart, Father, to be somebody that You're able to rest on.

00:25:24.640 --> 00:25:30.861
At my house, I make this house a place that He would be comfortable coming to.

00:25:30.861 --> 00:26:19.510
If He was to manifest in real form and knock on the door, would He open your door and look around and go, "Man, there's a lot of sin in here," or does He open your door and go, "I can come in here and have a glass of iced tea with Brandon because I feel comfortable"?

00:26:19.510 --> 00:26:25.533
Ladies and gentlemen, practice His presence.

00:26:25.533 --> 00:26:38.048
Father, I don't want anything to come through these eye gates that will offend You.

00:26:38.048 --> 00:26:41.168
Take captive of your thoughts.

00:26:41.168 --> 00:26:46.794
Men, don't be going around church lusting after women.

00:26:46.794 --> 00:26:58.880
You've got to have your eye gates and your mind pure before the Father.

00:27:04.786 --> 00:27:05.093
He can hear your thoughts.

00:27:05.093 --> 00:27:15.227
If you have thoughts that are bad, He'll say, "Brandon, check your thoughts.

00:27:15.227 --> 00:27:15.724
" Why?

00:27:15.724 --> 00:27:17.350
Because it's offensive.

00:27:17.350 --> 00:27:25.779
We're not perfect, but I'm trying to challenge you to come up higher.

00:27:25.779 --> 00:27:38.216
Diana and I have got our stuff we're going through just like everybody else, but it's the heart that is quick to repent and says, "Father, I need You.

00:27:38.216 --> 00:27:55.705
" Stop trying to box God in and being so small-minded that you think He has to operate in the way you think He's going to operate.

00:27:58.888 --> 00:28:03.535
God loves you and He wants relationship with you.

00:28:14.218 --> 00:28:23.279
He said, "Brandon, tell them to come unto me.

00:28:23.279 --> 00:28:46.493
" Matthew: "Come to me, all you who are weary and burdened, and I will give you rest.

00:28:46.493 --> 00:29:12.007
Take my yoke upon you and learn from me, for I am gentle and humble in heart, and you will find rest for your souls.

00:29:13.832 --> 00:29:22.654
For my yoke is easy and my burden is light.

00:29:22.654 --> 00:29:30.151
" Run to God when you sin; don't run from Him.

00:29:30.151 --> 00:29:36.387
Your sin is none of the devil's business.

00:29:37.453 --> 00:29:54.707
I come to Him with communion when I sin and say, "Father, at Your mercy seat, I bow myself in humility and say, Father, use me.

00:29:54.707 --> 00:30:03.460
Forgive me; wash me in Your blood; cleanse me from all unrighteousness.

00:30:03.460 --> 00:30:10.794
" The sin issue is already taken care of.

00:30:10.794 --> 00:30:32.320
He said if you confess your sins, He is faithful and just to forgive you of your sins and cleanse you from all unrighteousness.

00:30:32.320 --> 00:30:38.999
So I seek Him daily.

00:30:38.999 --> 00:30:56.569
I just felt it in my heart to spur you to have an intimate relationship with Him.

00:30:56.569 --> 00:30:58.660
Does He know you?

00:30:58.660 --> 00:31:03.839
My wife knows me; my kids know me.

00:31:03.839 --> 00:31:13.110
Do you look at Him as some kind of religious, far-out thing?

00:31:13.120 --> 00:31:19.654
You've got to take down that wall.

00:31:19.654 --> 00:31:28.293
"Come unto me and I will give you rest.

00:31:28.293 --> 00:31:30.824
" Lean into Him.

00:31:30.824 --> 00:31:34.740
Trust, lean on, rely on, and be confident in the Lord.

00:31:34.740 --> 00:31:56.075
Delight yourself also in the Lord, and He will give you the desires and secret petitions of your heart.

00:31:56.075 --> 00:32:52.000
Commit your way to the Lord; trust, lean on, rely on, and be confident also in Him, and He will bring it to pass.

00:32:52.000 --> 00:33:10.067
That's intimacy right there.

00:33:10.067 --> 00:34:16.473
Abraham staggered not at the promise of God through unbelief, but was strong in faith, giving glory to God.

00:34:16.473 --> 00:35:00.577
He was fully persuaded—that is confidence—that what God had promised, He was able also to perform.

00:35:00.577 --> 00:35:40.898
I'm not moved by what I see or hear; I'm only moved by what the word of God says.

00:36:02.960 --> 00:36:04.165
Jesus Christ, the same yesterday, today, and forever.

00:36:04.165 --> 00:36:27.000
If He did it 2,000 years ago, He's still doing it today.

00:36:27.000 --> 00:36:39.320
He's still healing and delivering.

00:36:39.320 --> 00:37:08.480
He gave us the authority to cast out devils and lay hands on the sick.

00:37:08.480 --> 00:37:56.263
We have got to come up higher in our thinking and say, "Father, I want more of You.

00:38:22.586 --> 00:38:23.280
I want more revelation of who You are in me.

00:38:23.280 --> 00:38:31.083
" Abraham was a friend of God.

00:38:31.083 --> 00:38:56.280
I want Him to call me friend.

00:38:56.280 --> 00:39:19.150
"I am a friend of God.

00:39:19.160 --> 00:39:37.780
He calls me friend.

00:39:37.780 --> 00:39:52.015
" Think about it.

00:39:52.015 --> 00:40:14.928
Who am I that You are mindful of me?

00:40:14.928 --> 00:40:30.059
That You hear me when I call?

00:40:30.059 --> 00:40:43.309
Is it true that You are thinking of me?

00:40:43.319 --> 00:40:53.053
Oh, how You love me.

00:40:53.053 --> 00:40:59.236
It's amazing.

00:41:34.177 --> 00:41:34.515
I am a friend of God.

00:41:34.515 --> 00:41:39.163
Does He call you friend today?

00:41:39.163 --> 00:41:43.129
My heart is for Him.

00:41:43.129 --> 00:41:46.867
Search me and know me today.

00:41:46.867 --> 00:41:50.903
Create in me a clean heart, O God.

00:41:57.530 --> 00:41:57.780
You are the potter; I am the clay.

00:41:57.780 --> 00:42:07.196
Help us not to get so stuck on these religious things.

00:42:19.120 --> 00:42:19.609
I want everything to do with relationship.

00:42:19.609 --> 00:42:33.585
Father, we lift up this body before You and we thank You that You were wounded for our transgressions, You were bruised for our iniquities, the chastisement of our peace was upon You, and with Your stripes, Lord, we are healed.

00:42:53.067 --> 00:42:53.600
We thank You that we don't have to be broke, busted, and disgusted anymore.

00:42:57.380 --> 00:43:09.764
We take this by faith and we are fully persuaded that Jesus Christ is our healer and our deliverer.

00:43:09.764 --> 00:43:29.059
Now, Lord, we take the blood and we apply the blood of Jesus over our children, my wife, and our finances.

00:43:29.059 --> 00:43:33.776
Forgive us, Father, of our sins.

00:43:37.839 --> 00:43:39.999
We enter in by the blood of the Lamb.

00:43:52.199 --> 00:43:52.560
We plead the blood of Jesus in the courts of heaven.

00:43:52.560 --> 00:44:00.045
When we mess up or stumble, we call out for the blood.

00:44:02.506 --> 00:44:03.546
It will never lose its power.

00:44:03.546 --> 00:44:10.583
Father, I apply it to our home.

00:44:10.583 --> 00:44:13.947
I plead the blood.

00:44:29.382 --> 00:44:29.628
Lord, You're beautiful; Your face is all I seek.

00:44:36.160 --> 00:44:42.560
And when Your eyes are on this child, Your grace abounds to me.

00:44:42.560 --> 00:44:46.040
Jesus, what a wonder You are.

00:44:49.010 --> 00:44:50.600
You are so gentle, so pure, and so kind.

00:44:52.559 --> 00:44:54.892
You shine like a bright morning star.

00:44:54.892 --> 00:44:59.060
Jesus, You're the sweetest name of all.

00:44:59.455 --> 00:45:10.255
You always hear me when I call; You lift me up each time I fall.

00:45:10.255 --> 00:45:28.271
Your name is like honey on my lips; Your spirit's like water to my soul; Your word is a lamp unto my feet.

00:45:28.271 --> 00:45:32.773
Jesus, holy and anointed one.

00:45:32.773 --> 00:45:45.1000
Holy, holy, holy is the Lord of hosts, who was and is and is to come.

00:45:45.1000 --> 00:45:48.794
Lose yourself in Him today.

00:45:48.794 --> 00:45:52.040
Sit at His feet.

00:45:53.863 --> 00:45:57.839
Everything that's bothering you—come unto Him.

00:45:57.839 --> 00:46:04.840
He's wanting to give you rest today.

00:46:04.840 --> 00:46:08.390
Jesus, Your presence makes me whole.

