We are thirsty; we need more.

00:46:18.392 --> 00:46:25.080
Fill our cup, Lord; we lift it up.

00:46:25.080 --> 00:46:29.465
Come and quench this thirsting of our soul.

00:46:29.465 --> 00:46:37.800
Bread of heaven, Feed us till we want no more.

00:46:37.800 --> 00:46:41.063
Lord, we worship You.

00:46:49.040 --> 00:46:49.367
Father, there are so many people and so many needs today.

00:46:49.693 --> 00:47:19.253
You inhabit the praises of Your people, and I thank You that we call them healed and whole and well in the name of Jesus, from the top of their head to the soles of their feet.

00:47:28.599 --> 00:47:29.359
I believe we receive what You said You'd do for us.

00:47:29.359 --> 00:47:33.903
With Your stripes, we're healed today.

00:47:50.260 --> 00:47:50.530
So Father, I agree with them that they're healed and whole and well.

00:47:50.530 --> 00:48:00.696
Delivered from all sickness and disease; delivered from the yoke of life and the bondage of sickness.

00:48:01.268 --> 00:48:09.013
We cast our care over onto You and lean confidently in You.

00:48:25.640 --> 00:48:25.871
We believe that today Your words are life to those that find them and health to all their flesh.

00:48:25.871 --> 00:48:36.180
Every single person who's believing for that right now, place your hand on where you're hurting.

00:48:40.909 --> 00:48:46.000
We speak healing, wholeness, and wellness over you right now in Jesus' name.

00:48:52.811 --> 00:48:58.994
Father, I thank You that the anointing is the burden-removing, yoke-destroying power, and You're removing every yoke.

00:49:18.553 --> 00:49:18.982
We take our care out of our prayer.

00:49:30.167 --> 00:49:30.813
We have the mind of Christ.

00:49:30.813 --> 00:49:41.400
We're not tormented in our thoughts anymore; we have the mind of Christ.

00:49:41.400 --> 00:49:46.149
Depression, anxiety, fear, loneliness, worry—we cast our care over onto You.

00:49:46.149 --> 00:49:56.497
God supplies all our needs according to His riches in glory by Christ Jesus.

00:49:56.497 --> 00:50:02.584
All their needs are met—spiritually, physically, financially, emotionally.

00:50:02.584 --> 00:50:11.200
Blessed in the city and the field, coming in and going out.

00:50:25.311 --> 00:50:25.599
Their household is blessed.

00:50:25.599 --> 00:50:35.619
Their marriages are whole; their children walk upright before You and will be saved.

00:50:35.619 --> 00:50:38.359
Wayward children are coming home.

00:50:38.359 --> 00:50:42.880
Satan, get your hands off of wayward children.

00:50:42.880 --> 00:50:47.267
No one's too far gone for Jesus to save.

00:50:51.870 --> 00:50:52.165
We call their minds renewed.

00:50:52.165 --> 00:51:01.446
You're the waymaker; You will bring it to pass.

00:51:01.446 --> 00:51:26.324
It may seem that the mountain of debt is on top of you, but I believe God's a waymaker and He's Jehovah Jireh—He will provide.

00:51:37.382 --> 00:51:37.671
We believe everything we put our hands to will prosper.

00:51:52.520 --> 00:51:52.914
We're calling those seeds in now.

00:51:52.914 --> 00:51:57.019
Harvest, come forth in Jesus' name!

00:52:09.519 --> 00:52:09.919
We call the prosperity angels to go right now and bring our harvest in.

00:52:09.919 --> 00:52:22.048
Good measure, pressed down, shaken together, and running over will men give unto us.

00:52:22.048 --> 00:52:26.466
You're a God of the overflow.

00:52:26.466 --> 00:52:34.230
This is a time of great overflow, not barely getting by.

00:52:34.230 --> 00:52:40.850
Thank You for supernatural increase over our houses today.

00:52:40.850 --> 00:52:43.217
I call your finances blessed.

00:52:43.217 --> 00:52:51.691
I call you to have more than enough.

00:52:51.691 --> 00:53:08.799
Give them creative ideas for jobs, raises, bonuses, benefits, sales, commissions, interest, income, rebates, returns, checks in the mail, gifts, and surprises.

00:53:08.799 --> 00:53:12.380
Finding money, bills paid off, bills decreased.

00:53:12.380 --> 00:53:26.884
This is a time like never before that the sowers and the reapers will go hand in hand.

00:53:26.884 --> 00:53:30.613
Abundant harvest is coming over them.

00:53:30.613 --> 00:53:40.274
We call those things that be not as though they were.

00:53:40.274 --> 00:53:45.800
We're blessed and prosperous; we're not barely getting by.

00:53:45.800 --> 00:53:48.160
Overflow belongs to us.

00:53:50.307 --> 00:53:51.820
The spirit of increase is on me.

00:53:51.820 --> 00:53:55.680
God is an abundant God.

00:53:55.680 --> 00:54:10.746
This is a time to soar and not be broke, to go forth and take the land with a back like a crowbar.

00:54:10.746 --> 00:54:28.767
We are those children who say we will take the land for Jesus and not do it barely half-cocked.

00:54:28.767 --> 00:54:33.460
We're taking back what the devil stole.

00:54:33.460 --> 00:54:37.319
Poverty stops with them.

00:54:43.018 --> 00:54:47.746
I will not be under the curse of poverty; poverty is a curse.

00:54:49.860 --> 00:54:50.520
It's not a blessing.

00:55:00.802 --> 00:55:01.776
"God keeps you poor to keep you humble"—that's ignorant.

00:55:01.776 --> 00:55:13.179
He is a God of more than enough.

00:55:13.179 --> 00:55:20.660
Don't allow the devil to steal and destroy anything.

00:55:20.660 --> 00:55:24.897
Poverty is a kill, steal, and destroy.

00:55:24.897 --> 00:55:29.211
True poverty—America does not know true poverty.

00:55:29.211 --> 00:55:33.620
Go to Haiti; there's true poverty in Haiti.

00:55:33.620 --> 00:55:41.943
That's true poverty—when your stomach's so swelled up and you're dying of hunger.

00:55:41.943 --> 00:55:45.520
Poverty is a curse.

00:55:49.805 --> 00:55:50.979
The body of Christ has to come out of stupid thinking.

00:55:50.979 --> 00:56:01.415
God wants you to have exceedingly, abundantly above all that you dare ask or think.

00:56:01.415 --> 00:56:08.839
If you sew a seed, God will provide for the need.

00:56:08.839 --> 00:56:17.427
You've got to believe God for big, like George Mueller.

00:56:18.819 --> 00:56:24.184
I know that story because my little girl watched it on VeggieTales.

00:56:24.184 --> 00:56:38.424
Believe God for big; stop believing for small.

00:56:38.424 --> 00:56:46.919
Thank You, Lord, that we have protection concerning viruses.

00:57:03.070 --> 00:57:03.465
We call that virus down in Jesus' name.

00:57:06.830 --> 00:57:09.559
We have the authority of the believer.

00:57:24.222 --> 00:57:24.559
A thousand shall fall at our side and ten thousand at our right hand, but nothing shall come nigh us.

00:57:24.559 --> 00:57:34.960
We'll not be afraid of any kind of pestilence or plagues.

00:57:34.960 --> 00:57:40.418
Jesus dwells on the inside of us.

00:57:40.418 --> 00:57:50.780
Who is this uncircumcised Philistine that he tries to defy the armies of the Lord?

00:57:50.780 --> 00:57:57.170
Concerning disease, plagues, cancers, and diabetes—who is this uncircumcised Philistine?

00:57:57.170 --> 00:58:05.119
Jehovah Jireh dwells on the inside of me.

00:58:06.079 --> 00:58:09.228
I lack no good thing.

00:58:18.466 --> 00:58:18.799
I renew my mind from stinking thinking today.

00:58:18.799 --> 00:58:27.533
We resist the devil and he must flee.

00:58:27.533 --> 00:58:33.568
Folks, you've got to be like a bulldog on a bone.

00:58:36.380 --> 00:58:42.190
"You are not going to steal from me anymore, devil!

00:58:42.200 --> 00:58:45.639
" Stand up on the inside.

00:58:56.703 --> 00:58:57.136
The waves try to knock you down, but I keep standing.

00:58:57.136 --> 00:59:10.937
I'm not moved by what I see or feel; I'm moved by what the word of God says.

00:59:10.937 --> 00:59:15.760
How bad do you want change?

00:59:18.474 --> 00:59:24.897
When you get some grit down inside you—"I will not be moved by this anymore!

00:59:24.897 --> 00:59:37.515
" When the police say your kid did something bad again—no, my child is turning around.

00:59:40.055 --> 00:59:42.545
I call him saved and delivered.

00:59:42.545 --> 00:59:49.650
I refuse to be moved by circumstances.

00:59:49.650 --> 01:00:00.380
My daughter is overcoming; she's healed and whole.

01:00:00.380 --> 01:00:09.050
When the doctor gives a bad report, I'm not moved by what I see.

01:00:14.359 --> 01:00:14.908
With His stripes, I am healed.

01:00:14.908 --> 01:00:19.940
The word is my foundation.

01:00:44.334 --> 01:00:44.961
I stagger not at the promise of God through unbelief.

01:00:44.961 --> 01:00:51.933
I am not moved by the report of the doctor.

01:00:51.933 --> 01:01:02.080
I will live a long life and declare the works of the Lord.

01:01:18.049 --> 01:01:20.155
He said He would satisfy me with long life, and I'm not satisfied yet.

01:01:20.155 --> 01:01:24.114
I hope this blessed you today.

01:01:24.114 --> 01:01:29.440
That's how you live by faith.

01:01:29.440 --> 01:01:33.729
Lean on Him and be confident in Him.

01:01:33.729 --> 01:01:42.940
He gives us a garment of praise for a spirit of heaviness.

01:01:42.940 --> 01:01:46.819
Worship Him in spirit and in truth today.

01:01:46.819 --> 01:01:51.079
My son said an hour and eight minutes.

01:01:51.079 --> 01:01:55.751
We'll do more prayer videos.

01:01:55.751 --> 01:01:57.527
Let's think bigger.

01:01:57.527 --> 01:02:06.019
God wants to use everybody, and we're in the end here.

01:02:06.899 --> 01:02:12.000
If you're new here, subscribe and click the notification bell.

01:02:19.240 --> 01:02:19.400
We pray for President Trump for special covering.

01:02:36.370 --> 01:02:38.320
Cover his mind and body.

01:02:38.520 --> 01:02:50.879
Thank You for President Trump today—that he will release the wealth from the deep for the body of Christ.

01:03:05.978 --> 01:03:09.299
Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

01:03:09.299 --> 01:03:11.377
Jesus loves you and we love you.

01:03:11.377 --> 01:03:14.819
God bless you all, and we'll see you again soon.

01:03:14.819 --> 01:03:16.559
Bye-bye.
